[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 0.18"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes affect Tails 0.18.

We **strongly** urge you to [[upgrade to Tails 0.19|news/version_0.19]]
as soon as possible in case you are still using an older version.

